{"tid":1131460,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"玩家打LOL劇透《復仇者4》帳號被封3天","createTime":"2019-04-29T16:07:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T04:36:49.000Z","uid":47905,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6040c22bdae4c14265ccc1865d043253fa9468df","tid":1131460,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:07:13.000Z","msg":"遊戲中也不要輕易爆雷！一名國外《英雄聯盟》的玩家在Reddit論壇上表示，自己因為在遊戲中向其他玩家爆雷目前超火熱電影《復仇者聯盟4》，帳號遭到Riot封鎖3天以示懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n這名玩家PO出Riot寄給自己的信件，上面寫著「我們知道你很興奮的想和其他人討論《復仇者聯盟4》，但是向其他玩家爆雷這行為一點都不酷，你的帳號將因為這個原因被禁止3天。」該名玩家表示，收到懲罰後的確有點惱怒，但是也完全認為自己活該。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/1556444706-3c5e6bab54402a5dd33f6132786a0061.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F1556444706-3c5e6bab54402a5dd33f6132786a0061.png&h=ff8a695e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nownews.com/news/20190428/3349902/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20190428%2F3349902%2F&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=d39cedfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nownews.com/news/20190428/3349902/</a><br />\n<br />\n唔理咩戲,咩國家,劇透撚真係人人喊打"},{"pid":"e2cd5b1c6822a760e7aadfe6ebf0f8ed50c0780b","tid":1131460,"uid":49391,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"封三日算少啦<br />\n起碼一個月先有阻嚇力"},{"pid":"f278181dd5684a6a24706fad50bb9db2bb342797","tid":1131460,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2cd5b1c6822a760e7aadfe6ebf0f8ed50c0780b","tid":1131460,"uid":49391,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:09:26.000Z","msg":"封三日算少啦<br />\n起碼一個月先有阻嚇力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"3日後再黎過"},{"pid":"247d7172eda6de92da77737a42da547ed31e1808","tid":1131460,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"抵呀"},{"pid":"9d7